headline: Moana 2 dominates record-breaking Thanksgiving box office
summary: Moana 2 returns $57.5 million on Thanksgiving Day, setting a new box office record for Disney (DIS). Experts are expecting a record-breaking Thanksgiving box office due to the combination of Moana 2, Gladiator II, and Wicked. In the spirit of last summer's "Barbenheimer" craze, moviegoers have been pairing the Gladiator sequel and Wicked together as "Glicked" as the next combination movie experience. Brian Sozzi and Julie Hyman take a closer look at what investors need to know. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here. This post was written by Naomi Buchanan.
